flowRoot.flowPara: Inputs:
data (global) a data.frame of the movement data
xyz (vector) a data.frame of xy or xyz coordinates
coords (data.frame) a character vector describing where the x,y,z (optional) coordinates are located in `data`
burst_list (vector) a list of named vectors describing multiple grouping variables
id (data.frame) a character string naming the 'id' field in `data`. Required if using data.frame inputs
burst_col (data.frame - optional) a character vector naming the other grouping columns in `data`.
active_burst (global) a character vector of the burst names to be 'active' to group data by for analysis
time (vector) a vector of time information, can be either POSIX or an integer
time_col (data.frame) a character string naming the column in `data` where the time information is located
error (vector - optional) a vector of error information for the movement data
error_col (data.frame - optional) a character string naming the column in `data` where the error information is located
crs a crs string from rgdal of the crs and projection information for the spatial data. Defaults to NA
zeroNA logical whether to convert 0s in spatial data into NAs. Defaults to FALSE.
